Build-Depends: cmake, debhelper-compat (= 13), pkg-config, libboost-dev, libboost-mpi-dev, libboost-system-dev, libboost-serialization-dev, libboost-thread-dev, libgtest-dev, libhdf5-mpi-dev, liblz4-dev, mpi-default-dev, latex2html, texlive-binaries, texlive-latex-base
Description: Fast Library for Approximate Nearest Neighbors FLANN is a library for performing fast approximate nearest neighbor searches in high dimensional spaces. It contains a collection of algorithms found to work best for nearest neighbor search and a system for automatically choosing the best algorithm and optimum parameters depending on the dataset.
Package-List: flann-doc deb doc optional arch=all libflann-dev deb libdevel optional arch=any libflann1.9 deb libs optional arch=any
